<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="esdrt.content">

<body>
  <metal:main fill-slot="content-core">
    <metal:content-core define-macro="content-core">

    <h2>Today's Summary</h2>

    <p>Observations: How many observations are still drafts, open in conclusion state and finished?</p>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Country</th>
          <th>Draft</th>
          <th>Open</th>
          <th>Conclusions</th>
          <th>Finished</th>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/observation_status_per_country">
          <td tal:content="country/country|string:Sum">Country</td>
          <td tal:content="country/draft|string:0">Draft</td>
          <td tal:content="country/open|string:0">Open</td>
          <td tal:content="country/conclusions|string:0">Conclusion</td>
          <td tal:content="country/closed|string:0">Finished</td>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Sector</th>
          <th>Draft</th>
          <th>Open</th>
          <th>Conclusions</th>
          <th>Finished</th>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/observation_status_per_sector">
          <td tal:content="country/sector">Sector</td>
          <td tal:content="country/draft|string:0">Draft</td>
          <td tal:content="country/open|string:0">Open</td>
          <td tal:content="country/conclusions|string:0">Conclusion</td>
          <td tal:content="country/closed|string:0">Finished</td>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>Q&amp;A: how many questions are in draft, open, pending, acknowledged?</p>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Country</th>
          <th>Draft</th>
          <th>Open</th>
          <th>Conclusions</th>
          <th>Finished</th>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/question_status_per_country">
          <td tal:content="country/country">Country</td>
          <td tal:content="country/draft|string:0">Draft</td>
          <td tal:content="country/open|string:0">Open</td>
          <td tal:content="country/conclusions|string:0">Conclusion</td>
          <td tal:content="country/closed|string:0">Finished</td>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Sector</th>
          <th>Draft</th>
          <th>Open</th>
          <th>Conclusions</th>
          <th>Finished</th>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/question_status_per_sector">
          <td tal:content="country/sector">Sector</td>
          <td tal:content="country/draft|string:0">Draft</td>
          <td tal:content="country/open|string:0">Open</td>
          <td tal:content="country/conclusions|string:0">Conclusion</td>
          <td tal:content="country/closed|string:0">Finished</td>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>How many observations will potentially require gap filling (initial checks)?</p>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Potential gap-filling</th>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <th tal:content="sector">1A</th>
          </tal:sectors>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/observation_highlights_pgf">
          <td tal:content="country/country">Sector</td>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <td tal:content="country/?sector">1A</td>
          </tal:sectors>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>How many observations will potentially be significant issues (step 1 annual review)?</p>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Potential significant issues</th>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <th tal:content="sector">1A</th>
          </tal:sectors>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/observation_highlights_psi">
          <td tal:content="country/country">Sector</td>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <td tal:content="country/?sector">1A</td>
          </tal:sectors>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>How many observations will potentially be technical corrections (step 2 annual review and comprehensive review)?</p>

    <table class="listing">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Potential technical corrections</th>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <th tal:content="sector">1A</th>
          </tal:sectors>
          <th>Sum</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr tal:repeat="country view/observation_highlights_ptc">
          <td tal:content="country/country">Sector</td>
          <tal:sectors repeat="sector view/get_sectors">
            <td tal:content="country/?sector">1A</td>
          </tal:sectors>
          <td tal:content="country/sum|string:0">Sum</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    </metal:content-core>
  </metal:main>

</body>
</html>

